Class FundingLabel

    LatentStateLabel
    public class FundingLabel
extends java.lang.Object
implements LatentStateLabel
    FundingLabel contains the Identifier Parameters referencing the Latent State of the named Funding Discount Curve. Currently it only contains the funding currency.
